Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.83,00:00:08.45,Caption,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.83,00:00:08.45,Caption2,,0,0,0,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.37,00:00:11.91,Caption,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.54,00:00:16.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yo, whatcha making?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.25,00:00:20.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A graduation album!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,00:00:21.91,Caption,,0,0,0,,Graduation Album
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.16,00:00:21.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A graduation album?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.08,00:00:24.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,For the School Living Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,00:00:25.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.41,00:00:27.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, that looks great!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.45,00:00:30.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Megu-nee said it'd be better if it were hand-drawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.79,00:00:35.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But your drawings are just so bad, Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.91,00:00:37.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wh-whaa...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.87,00:00:40.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're helping her with it too, Miki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.83,00:00:44.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Only if she does her part in our other activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.08,00:00:46.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, Miki's way better at drawing than Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.91,00:00:48.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,These are great!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.12,00:00:52.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Miki's reading a book here, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.16,00:00:54.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.33,00:01:00.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A close friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.41,00:01:07.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Class ended early that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.87,00:01:11.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but the sky was so pretty and blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.75,00:01:14.29,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,we figured it'd be a waste of a good day \Nto just head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.29,00:01:16.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So we stopped somewhere on our way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.33,00:01:18.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Miki!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.58,00:01:23.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.50,00:01:27.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Where do you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.12,00:01:29.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There's a book I'd like to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.50,00:01:31.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay, the bookstore it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.08,00:01:33.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Can we hit up the arcade after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.79,00:01:34.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.62,00:01:37.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,...cut to a camera on the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.37,00:01:39.04,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Let's take some pictures at the photo booth, too! \N...cut to a camera on the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.04,00:01:41.00,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,There's one with some new features! \NWhile the reason behind them is still unknown...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.00,00:01:42.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,While the reason behind them is still unknown...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.08,00:01:44.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,00:01:45.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,wait up, Kei!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,00:01:47.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
