Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,00:02:28.04,Caption,,0,0,0,,Houkago nara atarimae no koto
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,00:02:29.37,Caption,,0,0,0,,Saa sa, atsumare!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,00:02:31.25,Caption,,0,0,0,,Kossori kaeruna! (Kora!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,00:02:34.41,Caption,,0,0,0,,Bukatsu dou dane? Katsudou shichau ne!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.54,00:02:36.95,Caption,,0,0,0,,Asonderu nja arimasen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.95,00:02:40.83,Caption,,0,0,0,,Tadaima tte ano ko ga iu yo (Okaeri!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.83,00:02:44.00,Caption,,0,0,0,,Minna de ireba daijoubu (Bu!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.00,00:02:47.25,Caption,,0,0,0,,Everybody say: tomodachi de iyou ne
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.25,00:02:48.79,Caption,,0,0,0,,Shitai kara shitai nara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.79,00:02:50.70,Caption,,0,0,0,,Shitai toki shitai desho
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,00:02:52.04,Caption,,0,0,0,,Daisuki (Hai!)
