Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.16,00:02:58.20,Caption,,0,0,0,,24 jikan hashaideru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.66,00:03:01.62,Caption,,0,0,0,,Okujou ni wa akana taiyou
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,00:03:05.04,Caption,,0,0,0,,Kanari sakendemita (Genki desu!)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.04,00:03:08.04,Caption,,0,0,0,,Watashitachi wa koko ni imasu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,00:03:11.33,Caption,,0,0,0,,Koko ni wa yume wa chanto aru
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,00:03:14.75,Caption,,0,0,0,,Friend nara tomodachi desho (Sou da!)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,00:03:17.87,Caption,,0,0,0,,Sukitte itte mita (Daisuki!)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,00:03:24.00,Caption,,0,0,0,,Field Trip
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.41,00:03:29.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thank you, come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.62,00:03:34.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,00:03:36.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.75,00:03:38.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Seriously, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,00:03:42.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Man, I just love the mall!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.54,00:03:47.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You still have a CD player?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,00:03:51.25,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't make fun of me! \NThe sound is totally different!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.95,00:03:58.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Aww, you're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,00:04:01.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do you like CDs better, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.62,00:04:02.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,00:04:06.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh my, did you find a playmate, Taromaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,00:04:08.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sorry, he was just so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.62,00:04:11.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's alright. Thank you for playing with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,00:04:14.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Come on, say bye-bye to the nice girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,00:04:19.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,00:04:20.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,00:04:22.04,Caption,,0,0,0,,Western Books
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,00:04:25.37,Caption,,0,0,0,,Western Books
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,00:04:29.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wow, you can read this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,00:04:33.75,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I read the translated version, \Nso I wanted to know if I could read the original...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,00:04:41.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,00:04:45.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Attention all customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.04,00:04:48.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,An incident causing serious injury has occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,00:04:55.66,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Please follow the directions of our mall staff \Nas we work to control the situ-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,00:04:57.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, this is pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,00:04:58.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is that the fire alarm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.83,00:04:59.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait, for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.91,00:05:00.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,00:05:02.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We should go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.91,00:05:04.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, why's everyone stopped?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,00:05:06.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The escalator's off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,00:05:09.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I hear someone's going around attacking people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,00:05:12.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Doesn't look like we can get down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,00:05:13.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,00:05:21.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, is the elevator working?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.33,00:05:24.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't know, we just got here ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.45,00:05:25.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.83,00:05:27.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,00:05:29.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It hasn't moved from the first floor at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,00:05:36.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's going up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,00:05:39.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm sure this is all a big misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,00:05:41.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,00:05:53.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,00:05:54.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What was it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,00:06:13.25,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Do you think those people in \Nthe elevator were dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,00:06:16.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Probably, they had blood all over them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,00:06:20.20,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,That wouldn't happen in a fire \Nor a regular accident, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,00:06:32.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's the doggie from earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,00:06:34.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,00:06:36.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,K-Kei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,00:06:39.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is he hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,00:06:40.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,00:06:44.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, he looks like he's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.12,00:06:45.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So what's this blood from?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,00:07:12.50,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I didn't realize what had actually happened \Nuntil a little bit later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.75,00:07:19.87,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,But I did understand that it was something \Nthat would forever change our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,00:07:34.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,00:07:42.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's infectious. Like in the movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,00:07:48.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If it's a disease, then they can make a vaccine, a cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,00:07:51.70,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I'm sure some foreign country will \Nbring their military and come help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,00:07:54.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,00:07:57.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Well, there's no use in getting down about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,00:07:58.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,00:08:04.16,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,But no matter how long we waited, \Nnobody came for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.70,00:08:08.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There were no signs that help was coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,00:08:18.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What're you listening to, Kei?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.75,00:08:21.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,00:08:22.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.87,00:08:25.87,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,That's right, you can listen to \Nthe radio on that thing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,00:08:29.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.87,00:08:33.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But I haven't been able to get any stations on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,00:08:36.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Kei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,00:08:37.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,00:09:04.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I wanna go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.95,00:09:05.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.91,00:09:07.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What?! But it's dangerous out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,00:09:10.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But we don't know how much longer we'll be safe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,00:09:11.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Kei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,00:09:19.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay, Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.50,00:09:41.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,00:09:44.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,really do want to go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,00:09:51.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We've still got food and water here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.08,00:09:54.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's stay together until help comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.37,00:09:59.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They won't know we're here unless we go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,00:10:02.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And I haven't taken a shower in forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,00:10:06.83,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,We're lucky to have running water here, \Nand we can use as much as we want!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,00:10:09.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We're using a little washbin for a toilet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,00:10:10.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's so gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.66,00:10:18.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,00:10:22.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And we're going to run out of food eventually!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,00:10:23.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,00:10:25.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.91,00:10:30.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why is it always me? It makes me look so selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,00:10:33.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Kei...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.95,00:10:35.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm going to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.87,00:11:13.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I just got a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.25,00:11:18.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What, jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,00:11:21.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's a reeeally fun idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,00:11:24.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,00:11:26.20,Caption,,0,0,0,,Scoot
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,00:11:29.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,All three of us club members...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,00:11:32.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,All three of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,00:11:34.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.12,00:11:38.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My, what's the ruckus?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,00:11:46.08,Caption,,0,0,0,,Grumble
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,00:11:46.08,Caption2,,0,0,0,,Grumble
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,00:11:42.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My, my, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,00:11:46.08,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Kurumi-chan's karate chop \Nmade my hair antenna cave in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,00:11:47.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It did not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.70,00:11:49.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.12,00:11:50.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sniff!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.12,00:11:52.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's her fault for being so uppity!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,00:12:00.79,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,But isn't it much more fun if you've got \Nsomething good to look forward to tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,00:12:06.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay, just leave that kinda stuff for before we pass out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,00:12:08.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's right. Let's get to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,00:12:09.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.62,00:12:17.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Go to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,00:12:18.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Aw, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.62,00:12:20.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're keeping all of us up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,00:12:21.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Right, Ri-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.83,00:12:25.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ri-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.37,00:12:26.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Zzz...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.54,00:12:28.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's our Ri-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.95,00:12:30.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Zzz...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.25,00:12:44.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,00:12:47.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,00:12:52.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Going? You mean, going outside?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,00:12:53.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.45,00:12:55.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,00:13:01.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do you plan on staying here forever, Miki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.50,00:13:02.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,00:13:15.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Taromaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,00:13:23.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I should be fine if I go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.29,00:13:24.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Kei...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,00:13:32.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are you happy, living in here, shut away?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.33,00:13:37.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.58,00:13:39.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll definitely bring help back for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.45,00:13:43.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Until I'm back, hold on to this for me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.83,00:13:52.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.79,00:14:03.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,00:14:10.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,00:14:14.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.25,00:14:27.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,00:14:29.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.25,00:14:32.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,00:14:35.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Pick whatever canned food you want to put on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.37,00:14:36.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,00:14:38.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, canned beef!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,00:14:40.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I didn't know we still had some!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.54,00:14:43.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,G'morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,00:14:47.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kurumi-chan, look! Canned beef!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.00,00:14:48.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,O-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,00:14:50.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Starting the day off with beef!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,00:14:52.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What a luxury!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,00:14:53.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What is this, the 1930s?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,00:14:56.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Treasure it. That's our last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,00:15:02.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's eat it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,00:15:05.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You can have it, Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.16,00:15:09.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, it's the last one, so we have to share it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.16,00:15:14.16,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Alright, then we'll split the other cans \Ninto three parts, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,00:15:15.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,00:15:16.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,00:15:19.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.33,00:15:27.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.45,00:15:29.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're in a good mood this morning, Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.70,00:15:33.54,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Mm-hm, because I thought of \Nsuch a great idea last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.54,00:15:35.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My, what could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,00:15:39.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's go on a field trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,00:15:41.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A field trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,00:15:43.79,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's the \Nperfect season for a field trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,00:15:44.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.83,00:15:46.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a great idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.58,00:15:48.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's bad manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.29,00:15:49.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, whoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.75,00:15:56.00,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,And did you forget that the School Living Club rules \Nsay we can't leave school?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.50,00:16:01.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've realized something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.66,00:16:03.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We can't leave school,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.66,00:16:06.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but there's an exception to the rule!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,00:16:09.91,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,If we leave for school purposes, \Nthen it's not leaving at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.20,00:16:09.91,Caption,,0,0,0,,Tadah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.91,00:16:11.62,Caption,,0,0,0,,Tadah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,00:16:15.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Right, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,00:16:16.91,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I don't think that line of logic really works. \NRight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.91,00:16:19.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And clubs don't do field trips, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,00:16:22.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're so closed-minded, Kurumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,00:16:24.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We're leading the way with our club!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.83,00:16:31.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I see. Then let's write up the paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.79,00:16:34.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Megu-nee has to take a look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.04,00:16:34.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,00:16:37.33,Caption,,0,0,0,,School Living Club Field Trip
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,00:16:37.33,Caption2,,0,0,0,,A field trip is a school event, so I think
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.96,00:16:37.33,Caption3,,0,0,0,,it would work great for our club activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.96,00:16:37.33,Caption4,,0,0,0,,We can also learn a lot of things
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.96,00:16:37.33,Caption5,,0,0,0,,by going outside. Also it's really fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.96,00:16:37.33,Caption6,,0,0,0,,School Living Club Representative Yuki Takeya
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,00:16:37.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've already put the paperwork together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.45,00:16:42.08,Caption,,0,0,0,,School Living Club Field Trip
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.45,00:16:42.08,Caption2,,0,0,0,,A field trip is a school event, so I think
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,00:16:42.08,Caption3,,0,0,0,,it would work great for our club activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,00:16:42.08,Caption4,,0,0,0,,We can also learn a lot of things
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,00:16:42.08,Caption5,,0,0,0,,by going outside. Also it's really fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,00:16:42.08,Caption6,,0,0,0,,School Living Club Representative Yuki Takeya
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,00:16:42.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Alright, then she just has to look at this, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,00:16:43.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,00:16:45.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,00:16:46.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll go get Megu-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,00:16:51.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.79,00:16:53.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait for Megu-nee, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,00:16:55.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's leave it to Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.58,00:16:58.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My, you've gotten much more positive about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.54,00:17:01.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, plus Yuki seems to be doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,00:17:03.91,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,And there's some stuff I want \Nthat I can't get from around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,00:17:06.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And that's what's important in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,00:17:10.95,Caption,,0,0,0,,Teacherâ€™s Room
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.16,00:17:07.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Now, how will we get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,00:17:10.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I guess we'll have to use Megu-nee's car.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.04,00:17:15.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She said okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.37,00:17:18.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's great, Yuki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.58,00:17:20.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Alright, guess it can't be helped, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.70,00:17:24.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If we go in my car, all four of us will fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.95,00:17:27.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're gonna let us ride in your car, Megu-nee?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,00:17:31.37,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,But I'm a little nervous since I \Nhaven't driven in so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.37,00:17:33.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, then I'll drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,00:17:34.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.29,00:17:37.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You can drive, Kurumi-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,00:17:42.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's fine, I'm definitely a better driver than Megu-nee.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.25,00:17:44.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,00:17:45.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,H-h-hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,00:17:47.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry, Megu-nee.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,00:17:51.45,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Well, I think it'd be good for Kurumi \Nto get used to driving,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.45,00:17:53.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,just in case something happens, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.54,00:17:55.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Th-that is true...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,00:17:57.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But when did you get your license?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,00:17:59.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ha! Ha! Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,00:18:01.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan, can you go get the car keys?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,00:18:02.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,00:18:05.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,M-my car...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,00:18:19.04,Caption,,0,0,0,,School
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,00:18:19.04,Caption2,,0,0,0,,Get down from here Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,00:18:19.04,Caption3,,0,0,0,,Cooking classroom
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,00:18:19.04,Caption4,,0,0,0,,Parking lot Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Front entrance
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,00:18:19.04,Caption5,,0,0,0,,Field
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.00,00:18:14.79,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,The safe place closest to the parking lot is the \Ncooking room right next to the second floor barricade.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,00:18:19.04,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Taking a ladder down from there \Nwould give us the shortest path to the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,00:18:21.79,Caption,,0,0,0,,School
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,00:18:21.79,Caption2,,0,0,0,,Get down from here Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,00:18:21.79,Caption3,,0,0,0,,Parking lot
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,00:18:21.79,Caption4,,0,0,0,,Field
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,00:18:21.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Can you sprint there with your shovel on your back?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.79,00:18:22.91,Caption,,0,0,0,,I can
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.79,00:18:22.91,Caption2,,0,0,0,,I can
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.79,00:18:22.91,Caption3,,0,0,0,,School
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.79,00:18:22.91,Caption4,,0,0,0,,Parking lot
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.79,00:18:22.91,Caption5,,0,0,0,,Field
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.79,00:18:22.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I can, I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,00:18:24.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,00:18:26.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are you all ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.95,00:18:28.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We can go, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,00:18:31.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here's the key to Megu-nee's car!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.70,00:18:33.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,00:18:34.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.95,00:18:37.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yup, I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.25,00:18:59.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.37,00:19:16.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They're doing construction on the stairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,00:19:17.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,00:19:53.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And on the entrance to the school?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,00:19:54.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.37,00:19:58.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Everyone's in class, so stay quiet, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.75,00:19:59.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.29,00:20:02.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Kurumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.04,00:20:09.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Crap! Which one is Megu-nee's?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.33,00:20:14.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Calm down, calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.45,00:20:26.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,00:20:28.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,00:20:37.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm... really...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.70,00:20:39.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,sorry... 'bout...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,00:20:41.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.33,00:20:54.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hold on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,00:20:56.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait, seatbelts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.08,00:20:57.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hold on, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.58,00:21:00.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Try not to dent my car, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,00:21:05.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Kurumi-chan, are you really okay to drive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.70,00:21:10.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's different than what I'm used to, but I can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,00:21:11.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Different?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,00:21:15.20,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I'm used to using a gamepad \Ninstead of a steering wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.83,00:21:18.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait, you mean a video game...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,00:21:21.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I told you, it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.62,00:21:24.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Just watch my awesome spinout!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.33,00:21:26.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't spinout!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.16,00:21:28.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My poor car!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.04,00:21:31.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Kurumi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.00,00:21:32.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.37,00:21:38.62,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,The road's all bumpy! \NAre they doing construction here, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.62,00:21:39.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We've got an opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.66,00:21:50.66,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,It was like the ending of a movie \NI saw a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.54,00:21:58.12,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Two people jumped in a car and \Ndrove off towards the distant horizon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,00:22:03.04,Caption,,0,0,0,,When you were by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.16,00:22:03.37,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,They'd thrown their lives behind and were \Nstarting off on a new journey in the evening sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.12,00:22:06.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That kind of movie.
